        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "source": "SMI",
      "text": "(Heb. oren), only in (Isaiah 44:14) As the true ash is not a native of Palestine, some understand this to be a species of pine tree. Perhaps the larch (Laryx europaea) may be intended.",
